| MkInstAll
| Make all the standalone variants of !SoundFX

Dir <Obey$Dir>

Set OldInstall$Dir <Install$Dir>
Set OldUserIf <UserIf>

Alias SoundFXBuild set userif %%0|mset install$dir |<build$dir>.install.%%0|mmkdir |<install$dir>|mamu install THROWBACK=-throwback

SoundFXBuild nc2
SoundFXBuild mpt
SoundFXBuild stb3

Set Install$Dir <OldInstall$Dir>
Set Locale <OldLocale>
